<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1003240' id='t-1003240'>then we need to reimagine our task.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1007120' id='t-1007120'>Our task is to create the space</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1009799' id='t-1009799'>where everybody's slices of genius</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1012440' id='t-1012440'>can be unleashed and harnessed,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1016960' id='t-1016960'>and turned into works
of collective genius.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
17:10
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1019720' id='t-1019720'>Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
